   "source": [
    "## Example: Top Positive and Negative SHAP Bits\n",
    "\n",
    "This example shows how to retrieve the most important fingerprint bits for one explained sample, split into positive and negative contribution lists.\n",
    "\n",
    "Run this after you have generated SHAP values (for example from `shap_ex.explain(...)` or `explain_smiles_with_shap(...)`)."
   ]
  },
